{"tid":1789723,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"英國外交部發表最新聲明 指一直關注香港變化 呼籲以政治對話解決問題","createTime":"2019-12-19T13:12:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-20T00:46:20.000Z","uid":133680,"like":7,"dislike":38,"uniUserReply":46,"replies":[{"pid":"dd6feae9858b5e76983110ace8e897265c5bca4f","tid":1789723,"uid":133680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T13:12:27.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.gov.uk/government/news/foreign-secretary-statement-on-the-sino-british-joint-declaration\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.gov.uk%2Fgovernment%2Fnews%2Fforeign-secretary-statement-on-the-sino-british-joint-declaration&d=d86Hk5Pgd4X%2FjIl3nTqvfHQc4T2II2f942UkEibGql8%3D&h=b4620a45\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.gov.uk/government/news/foreign-secretary-statement-on-the-sino-british-joint-declaration</a><br />\nForeign Secretary statement on the Sino British Joint Declaration<br />\nEnglish中文<br />\nForeign Secretary Dominic Raab statement on the 35th anniversary of the Sino British Joint Declaration.<br />\n<br />\nPublished 19 December 2019<br />\nFrom:<br />\nForeign &amp; Commonwealth Office and The Rt Hon Dominic Raab<br />\n<br />\nThirty five years ago today, on 19 December 1984, the Governments of the United Kingdom and China reached an agreement on the question of Hong Kong. The Sino British Joint Declaration, as it is known, was registered with the UN on 12 June 1985 as a legally-binding international treaty that remains in force today.<br />\n<br />\nCommenting on the anniversary, the Foreign Secretary Dominic Raab said:<br />\n<br />\nThis agreement between the UK and China made clear that Hong Kong&rsquo;s high-degree of autonomy, rights and freedoms would remain unchanged for 50 years. The undertakings made by China, including the right to freedom of expression, an independent judiciary and the rule of law are essential to Hong Kong&rsquo;s prosperity and way of life.<br />\n<br />\nHong Kong is experiencing its greatest period of turmoil since the handover. As a co-signatory of the Joint Declaration, the UK takes these commitments seriously and supports their implementation through the &lsquo;One Country, Two Systems&rsquo; framework. The only way to guarantee Hong Kong&rsquo;s future success and stability is by respecting these and addressing the legitimate concerns of the people of Hong Kong through meaningful political dialogue."},{"pid":"96841a8774c13ad44d6d0ce3706b40daa85b9676","tid":1789723,"uid":249263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T13:12:57.000Z","msg":"Twitter戰線:要令星火事件上到國際！！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1789690\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1789690</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">幫手入去將星火推到上國際</span>"},{"pid":"0dd1a5325be803e62defa1da5acb2994669a476d","tid":1789723,"uid":303361,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T13:13:08.000Z","msg":"達交部<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8bd2a2913419657b0396f53629548a7ff9889110","tid":1789723,"uid":258649,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T13:13:25.000Z","msg":"迖哥原來係英國高層<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"002a84848e41662afac13849613df51b6d08c985","tid":1789723,"uid":29080,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T13:14:22.000Z","msg":"一直關注<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n天佑香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1d325720cbc430dd390b02b20ac23854066b9a25","tid":1789723,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"201